<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bid-v">bid <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɪd/    美 /bɪd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-bid-bid-vi-vt">1.★ <strong>(bid, bid) vi &amp; vt (拍卖时) 出 (价)；投标：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He <strong>bid</strong> $100,000 <strong>for</strong> an old painting. 
他出价10万美元买一幅古画。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They <strong>bid against</strong> each other <strong>on / for</strong> a new project.
他们为一个新项目相互竞标。</p></div></div>